name: Kimberly Nobody (age slider)
description:
Follow me to make sure you see new styles, poses and Nobodys when I post them. Things move fast on this site, it's easy to miss.

I've gotten better at making these. There's now flexibility to age the Nobody younger or older and still keep a consistent face. Meet Kimberly Nobody, this person doesn't exist. You may think she looks like someone you know, but she isn't. Just the imprecise nature of diffusion. Most images were generated using the legendary A to Zovya RPG Artist's Tools models. Some poses helped by zPoses

If you need a consistent character but don't want a known celebrity, Kimberly is your gal. Kimberly prefers to have long wavy blonde hair (sometimes pink). She's a free spirit so be sure to prompt whatever clothes you want her to wear.

Follow me for more of the Nobody family coming soon for 1.5 and 2.1.

Click the zNobody tag for more, or the Nobody tag to see other's contributions.

Do you have requests? I've been putting in many more hours lately with this. That's my problem, not yours. But if you'd like to tip me, buy me a beer. Beer encourages me to ignore work and make AI models instead. Tip and make a request. I'll give it a shot if I can. Here at Ko-Fi
